initialize.sh vendors the AmmClient sources here:
  - AmmClient/        real file copies of AmmClient.{c,h} network.{c,h}
                      protocol.{c,h} tools.{c,h}  (compiled into the node)
  - AmmarServer/      a full clone, only created when no dev tree / vendored
                      copy is available to source the files from
Both are git-ignored (see .gitignore); regenerate them with ./initialize.sh.
